data.description: Beautiful Home In Silver Ridge Swim/Tennis Community. This home features 3 bedrooms and 2 1/2 baths. It has hardwood flooring on the main level and carpeting in the other areas of the house. The family room has a fireplace accented with a lovely ceiling fan. You also have a eat-in kitchen with a chandelier for a nice dinning experience. The yard is fenced in with a patio area to enjoy nice evenings outdoors. The yard is large and private. This location is minutes from shopping and the Silver Comet Trail. The HOA fees include maintenance of the front lawn and swim/tennis
